lead_paragraph: After squandering a second successive chance to clinch the World Series, Cleveland Indians manager Terry Francona tried to claim an edge for his team going into Wednesday's deciding Game Seven.

headline.print_headline: Indians Look to Bullpen for Edge in Finale
